{
  "_doc": "Curated source URLs for bank Faaliyet Raporlari (annual/activity reports). Franchise lane (src/faaliyet). Per bank: name, ir_page (investor-relations landing), and reports{<fiscal_year>:{tr:<url>, en:<url?>}}. Annual cadence (FY ending 31 Dec). ir_page is seeded from audit_report_urls.json; the per-year report URLs MUST be curated by hand (banks publish the annual report on a different page than the quarterly BRSA statements, and naming changes each year). Point tr/en at the standalone Faaliyet Raporu PDF, NOT the Surdurulebilirlik (sustainability) report.",
  "_updated": "2026-07-11",
  "_coverage": "FY2025 added 2026-07-11. 25/31 banks have BOTH FY2024 + FY2025; 3 have FY2025 only (TFKB / AKTIF / PASHA — FY2024 not hosted on-site). 28/31 have FY2025. Remaining gaps (no report URL either year): HSBC (wholesale; .vsf-only, IR page not machine-fetchable), ATBANK (trade-finance; only BRSA statements published, no standalone faaliyet raporu found), KLNMA (development bank; no retail franchise, only a third-party mirror surfaced). Dev/investment/trade-finance banks (KLNMA/AKTIF/PASHA/ATBANK/EXIM/TSKB) yield little/no retail-franchise data by design, so empty/thin extractions there are expected. FY2025 URLs verified 2026-07-11 (Referer-gated domains TSKB/QNBFB/PASHA/VAKIFK confirmed via IR-page listing — the CI fetch applies the per-bank Referer map).",
